Title: Prakroma Kumkumadi Thailam(5 ml)
Description: Kumkumadi tailam is a unique blend of oils and ayurvedic herbs formulated to help skin look young and healthy. It is the traditional way of including facial oils in your regular skin care. And the best part is you need not prepare an effective concoction by mixing up various oils and essential oils. This ‘miracle in a bottle’ already has around 16 highly potent ingredients which will help you with probably everything under the sun. The saffron, sandalwood, turmeric, lotus pollen, jasadbhasma, vetiver, licorice and several other beneficial ingredients make it the ‘Wonder Boy’ of facial oils.Benefits of Kumkumadi Tailam:Illuminates skin: Glowing skin and brighter complexion is the primary benefit of using this ayurvedic concotion. Anti-bacterial and antioxidant features of saffron keeps your skin healthy and also gives a brighter tone by removing tan from your face.Young and healthy skin: Kumkumadi Tailam is famous for it's anti-ageing properties from time immemorial. Every woman needs to have this serum in her kitty once she crosses 30. With a regular face massage, will boost your anti-ageing skin care routine and keep it young and toned.Flawless Skin: Kumkumadi Tailam also helps in correcting skin problems like spots, dark circles, acne, blemishes, etc. Turmeric and sandalwood, along with other ingredients, keep the skin problem free and helps to control blemishes and lighten the spots.Sun protection: Jasadbhasma in this serum acts as a natural sunscreen against harmful and damaging sun rays.Clear Skin: Tailam is the best way to nourish, soothe and brighten the skin in one go.Gets rid of dark circles: Regular use of the tailam will lighten and brighten the skin around your eyes.Ways to Use Kumkumadi Tailam: The easiest and the most common way to use this Tailam is as a regular facial massage. Take about 10-12 drops of the oil and apply on your clean face. Start massaging your face in gentle and upward strokes for 5-10 minutes. Leave it on for further 10 minutes and then wash it off with water.You can also apply 3-5 drops of the oil at night in place of your night cream.Mix a couple of drops in your face packs to amp up the moisturizing benefits of the pack.Apply it directly on dark circles or scars before going to bed to quickly lighten the skin.

Title: Affable Anti Wrinkle cream(50 g)
Description: Product DescriptionAffable brings you an exquisite range of skin care products which can leave you with a healthy glow after prolonged use. This Affable wrinkle reduction Anti-Ageing Cream can rejuvenate your ageing skin and add a youthful look to your appearance.This Affable Wrinkle reduction cream can be your every day solution if you want to get rid of the different signs of ageing, which includes wrinkles, fine lines, skin dryness and loss of skin firmness. Enriched with extracts from natural ingredients like Camellia oleifera Extracts, this skin care product can enliven your skin and bring back the healthy shine you have always desired.Vitamin C consists of 40 antioxidant compounds which prevents ageing, removes toxins and stimulates blood circulation of the skin. Being an active ingredient of this anti-ageing cream, it can enhance the elasticity of your skin and help to maintain your youthfulness. Vitamin B6 and antioxidants can prevent skin damage, increase skin radiance, and smoothen the texture of your skin. The anthocyanins can help in building up the connective tissues and destroys harmful enzymes which cause lifeless fine lines and wrinkles. The presence of gentle cleansing agent can help you maintain the natural glow of your skin, and give you reason enough to buy Affable wrinkle reduction cream. Being simple and easy to use, the product comes in a 50g pack and can be a must buy for all women exposed to hectic and strenuous schedules.From the ManufacturerDescription:It is enriched with active natural ingredients like active essence of cherries, combined with bilberry extract which helps firm skin and ginger which helps boost the natural process of skin’s regeneration.Affable Wrinkle Reduction visibly reduces wrinkles and fine lines and to help make the skin feel firmer and smoother.
